    public class BeanMapperImpl<A extends Storable,B extends BaseBean>
extends ma.glasnost.orika.CustomMapper<A,B>
implements BeanMapper<A,B>
    This is a bean ma.glasnost.orika custom mapper. Only the properties having same names are copied. If nested objects are supposed to be mapped, please implement a BeanMapper interface to do it manually.
